## Proposed System Architecture & Layer Breakdown

### Layer 1: Identity & Compliance Infrastructure
- **Contracts**: `IdentityRegistry.sol`, `IdentityRegistryStorage.sol`, `TrustedIssuersRegistry.sol`, `ClaimTopicsRegistry.sol`, `ComplianceModule.sol`
- **Indexed Entities**:
  - `sbt_identities`: SBT Claims, ON-CHAIN DIDs, country codes, investor verification levels.
  - `wallet_compliance_states`: Wallet restrictions (`isFrozen`, `investorRestrictions`), freeze timestamps, restriction reasons.
  - `trusted_issuers`: Registered trusted SBT issuers and claim topics.
  - `compliance_audit_logs`: On-chain compliance enforcement events, rule violations, circuit breaker pauses.

### Layer 2: Asset Tokenization & Carbon Metadata Infrastructure
- **Contracts**: `AssetToken.sol` (ERC-3643 / ERC-20), `AssetRegistry.sol`, `CarbonAssetMetadataStore.sol`, `CarbonBatchManager.sol`
- **Indexed Entities**:
  - `indexed_assets`: Asset ID, Name, Symbol, Decimals, Category (`REAL_ESTATE`, `CARBON_CREDIT`, `FINE_ART`, `COMMODITIES`, `PRIVATE_EQUITY`), Contract Address, Vault Address.
  - `carbon_asset_metadata`: Verra / Gold Standard Project ID, methodology, project type, vintage year, total credit quantity, serial number ranges, 32-byte document SHA-256 hashes (`pddHash`, `verificationReportHash`, `monitoringReportHash`, `issuanceCertificateHash`, `immobilizationProofHash`), ICVCM CCP flags.
  - `carbon_vintage_batches`: Batch ID, vintage year, total credits, available credits, retired credits, mint txHash.

### Layer 3: Vault Yield, NAV Valuation & Fee Infrastructure
- **Contracts**: `VaultFactory.sol`, `SyncVaultTemplate.sol`, `AsyncVaultTemplate.sol`, `NAVOracle.sol`, `FeeEngine.sol`
- **Indexed Entities**:
  - `indexed_vaults`: Vault Address, Asset Token Address, Category, Vault Type (`SYNC` / `ASYNC`), TVL, Total Vault Shares, Decimals.
  - `vault_deposits_withdrawals`: Investor Address, Vault Address, Transaction Type (`DEPOSIT` / `WITHDRAWAL`), USDC Amount, Shares Minted/Burned, Entry NAV per share, TxHash, Block Number.
  - `async_settlement_queue`: Request ID, Investor, Shares, Assets, Status (`PENDING`, `PROCESSED`, `CLAIMED`, `CANCELLED`, `FAILED`), Request Time, Settlement Time.
  - `nav_attestations`: Asset ID, NAV Value (USD), Valuation Method, Submitter/Verifier Address, Valuation Date, Attestation TxHash, Dispute Status.
  - `fee_accrual_logs`: Vault Address, Fee Type (`MANAGEMENT`, `PERFORMANCE`, `ENTRY`, `EXIT`), Fee BPS, Calculated Amount, Recipient Wallet, HWM (High-Water Mark) / Hurdle Rate Checkpoints.

### Layer 4: Secondary Settlement & Beneficial Ownership Register (BOR v2)
- **Contracts**: `OwnershipSyncManager.sol` (BOR v2), `CarbonRetirementManager.sol`, `LifecycleExitManager.sol`
- **Indexed Entities**:
  - `beneficial_ownership_register`: Investor Wallet Address, Investor Handle (`@handle`), Asset Token Address, Token Balance, Pro-Rata Vault Ownership %, Entry NAV, Total Value USD, Last Updated Block.
  - `p2p_settlement_logs`: Swap ID, Sender Address (`@senderHandle`), Receiver Address (`@receiverHandle`), Token Address, Quantity Transferred, Settlement Price USD, Settlement Type (`P2P_DVP`, `PRIMARY_MINT`), TxHash, Block Number.
  - `carbon_retirements`: Retirement ID, Retiree Address (`@handle`), Amount Retired, Beneficiary Name, Retirement Reason, Certificate Hash / IPFS CID, Status (`SUCCESS`, `PENDING_RETRY`), Retry Count, TxHash.
  - `asset_lifecycle_exits`: Exit ID, Token Address, Vault Address, Liquidation USDC Pool Amount, Total Shares Locked, Payout Per Share, Distribution TxHash.

