## 3. Implementation Steps & File Modifications

### Component 1: `crats-indexer/prisma/schema.prisma`
- Append 8 Layer-specific database models (`SbtIdentity`, `WalletComplianceState`, `CarbonAssetMetadata`, `CarbonBatch`, `NavAttestation`, `FeeAccrualLog`, `BeneficialOwnerRecord`, `P2pSettlementLog`, `CarbonRetirementRecord`, `AssetLifecycleExit`).
- Run `npx prisma generate` & `npx prisma migrate dev`.

### Component 2: Indexer Event Ingestion Engine (`crats-indexer/src/ingestion/`)
- `eventIngestionService.js`: Listens to block header events on Sepolia (`chainId: 11155111`).
- Parses topics for all CRATS EVM events (`Transfer`, `SyncRouted`, `NAVUpdated`, `FeeAccrued`, `RetirementCompleted`, `LifecycleExitInitiated`).

### Component 3: Projection Processing Engine (`crats-indexer/src/projections/`)
- `borProjection.js`: Updates `beneficial_owner_records` on every token transfer and P2P swap.
- `navProjection.js`: Updates `nav_attestations` and re-calculates vault share pricing.
- `feeProjection.js`: Checkpoints continuous management fee accruals and performance High-Water Marks (HWM).
- `carbonRetirementProjection.js`: Tracks carbon batch retirements and retry queues.

### Component 4: High-Performance GraphQL & REST API Server (`crats-indexer/src/api/`)
- Exposes query endpoints:
  - `GET /api/v1/bor/:tokenAddress`: Returns Beneficial Ownership Register for an asset with `@handles`.
  - `GET /api/v1/vaults/:vaultAddress/accounting`: Returns AUM, NAV, Treasury vs Vault balances, fee accruals.
  - `GET /api/v1/carbon/metadata/:assetId`: Returns carbon metadata, serial ranges, and 32-byte DMS document hashes.
  - `GET /api/v1/p2p/history`: Returns secondary settlement audit trail.

